OL,3,CChildren as young as 14 paid up to
OL,4,C#600 to steal iPhones for organised
OL,5,Cgangs
OL,7,FThe head of the Metropolitan Police
OL,8,Fhas told Good Morning Britain that
OL,9,Fchildren as young as 14 are being
OL,10,Fexploited by criminal gangs and paid
OL,11,Fup to #600 to steal mobile phones.
OL,13,FThe youngsters are often recruited on
OL,14,Fsocial media and offered incentives
OL,15,Ffor the biggest hauls.
OL,17,FThe figures have been revealed
OL,18,Ffollowing a year long operation by the
OL,19,FMet which saw 10,000 fewer phones
OL,20,Fsnatched from people in the capital.
