OL,5,Cgangs
OL,7,FAs part of the crackdown police have
OL,8,Fbeen breaking down doors in early
OL,9,Fmorning raids looking for suspected
OL,10,Fphone snatchers.
OL,12,FOfficers found a 16-year-old who was
OL,13,Fjust one of 247 suspects arrested in
OL,14,Flast month alone.
OL,16,FThe teen is thought to be part of a
OL,17,Fgang who have stolen over a thousand
OL,18,Fphones with members as young as 14
OL,19,Fhired through social media.
