OL,3,CChildren as young as 14 paid up to
OL,4,C#600 to steal iPhones for organised
OL,5,Cgangs
OL,7,FThey can earn up to #600 per phone
OL,8,Fthey snatch off the street.
OL,10,FAs well as dawn raids drones follow
OL,11,Fsuspects in the sky and on the street
OL,12,Fspecial e-bikes are ready to chase.
OL,14,FMet Commissioner Sir Mark Rowley said
OL,15,Ftech companies needed to make phones
OL,16,Fimpossible to reactivate and sell on.
OL,18,F"That would break the business model
OL,19,Fbecause it would take the value of of
OL,20,Fthose stolen phones," Sir Mark Rowley
OL,21,Fsaid.
