OL,7,F"We know there is more to do and we're
OL,8,Fnot complacent about it.
OL,10,F"But the team here in north London
OL,11,Fhave done a fantastic job."
OL,13,FThe tech companies say they work
OL,14,Ftirelessly to ensure the strongest
OL,15,Fpossible deterrence to criminals
OL,16,Ftargeting phones.
